      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KIARNI PHOENIX (1) broke from this box and finished in the placings when a 4.5 lengths third in fast time (30.26) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Looks the one to beat on best. ZIPPING HAGEN (2) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (25.26) at Maitland. One of the main contenders. ZIPPING VIVID (7) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from five starts. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.27) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 7 length fifth. Can hit the frame with the right run. LAST SHOT RIPPER (4) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
